      <title>由于就业数据扰乱降息押注，美元触及枢轴前水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/dollar-hits-near-pre-pivot-level-as-job-data-roils-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在井喷式就业报告发布后，美元出现两周来最大涨幅，将美元推回到美联储12月转向以及押注即将降息之前的错误水平之前的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/dollar-hits-near-pre-pivot-level-as-job-data-roils-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 16:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据火爆后新兴市场货币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/china-stocks-lag-emerging-market-peers-by-most-in-11-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业报告井喷，引发了人们对美联储将推迟降息至 3 月甚至 5 月之后的担忧，新兴市场货币周五暴跌。土耳其央行行长辞职后，土耳其里拉当天晚些时候下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/china-stocks-lag-emerging-market-peers-by-most-in-11-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 11:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
